== 評價 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度33%，基於118條評論，平均分為4.8/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/johnny_english/ |title=Johnny English Movie Reviews, Pictures – Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |date= |accessdate=2010-08-12 |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319164457/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/johnny_english |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到51分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/johnny-english|title=Johnny English Reviews, Ratings, Credits, and More at Metacritic|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|date=|accessdate=2011-11-20|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315150848/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/johnny-english|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.1分，差評居多。

